a:5:{s:5:"title";s:61:"Salesmate email widget adds delivery and tracking visibility";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:396:"<p>Salesmate updated the email widget inside Contacts and Deals to display delivery status, tracking info, and the channel used—reducing the need to check separate logs.</p>
<p>Where to find it: Contacts/Deals → Email Widget.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://www.salesmate.io/blog/january-2026-release-notes/">https://www.salesmate.io/blog/january-2026-release-notes/</a></p>
